 self-staging - the development of photography from the 19(th) Century to the modern age.  afunded by Deutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG) (Graduiertenkolleg)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAbstraktion. 4aKunst. 4aKunstgeschichte des 19. Jahrhunderts. 4aKunstgeschichte des 20. Jahrhunderts. 4aKunstwissenschaft. 4aModerne. 4aPiktorialismus. 7aART / History / Modern (late 19th Century to 1945).2bisacsh  aAbstraction.  aArt History of the 19th Century.  aArt History of the 20th Century.  aArt.  aFine Arts.  aModernity.2 aDeutsche Forschungsgemeinschaft (DFG) (Graduiertenkolleg)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2018z9783110603088oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839441930zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839441930423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839441930/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DPKb2018